                     <interp inst="t17770409-4-off17" type="offenceSubcategory" value="grandLarceny"></interp>
               stealing a pair of thread lace lappets, value 30 s.
            </rs> the property of 
               
                  <persName id="t17770409-4-victim33" type="victimName">
                     Ann
                      Gifford
                  <interp inst="t17770409-4-victim33" type="surname" value="Gifford"></interp>
